07/04/2004
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- BiH's Investigative Documentation Centre, Croatia's Centre for Peace Studies and Serbia's Humanitarian Law Centre signed an agreement Tuesday (6 April) on war crimes documentation. It envisions co-operation in the gathering and exchange of information about war crimes perpetrators. Members of victims' families, prisoner-of-war associations and NGOs attended the signing ceremony. (B92, FENA - 06/04/04)
